description:
TAPAK

Thank you for visiting this link. This is my fourth drop of NFT work, the title is TAPAK or imprint, this is a series of works from the three NFT works that I have dropped and are available on Hicetnunc before. tell the same thing regarding self-response and true discovery of what we are really aware of and sow all this time, then confronted with all the novelties will it help us grow or will we be uprooted just because we are tempted.
In modern life, it seems that there are very strong things that try to lull and uproot the human feeling as a whole human being, sometimes it is too noisy and scrambles for the achievements and values that are transient which often makes us fall into and even dissolve in the scheme of the cradle of the world. But if patience is not wrong or detrimental why don't we accept it as a way of life?
_
5400px X 5400px
If you collect or purchase a token of this work you have the right to:
- Publish the work that you collect through your social media account by including the credit of the creator's name and the link to his social media account or the link that is linked to the creator.
- Print this work in physical print format for personal display purposes (not intended to commercialize this asset)
- Presenting this work at a digital exhibition event on a specific platform that accommodates it, while still giving credit to the creator.
- The rest is the right to enjoy it and I am happy if you are willing to write your point of view from my work and you publish and share stories for this work.

Please share good things.
Kind Regards
Wicaksono Azis
